{"tid":1279263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【老中青WE CONNECT】 咁多位自稱廢老、廢中既新會員入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-02T15:37:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T13:54:19.000Z","uid":154486,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"50f4c3f72fc9d5f93c5fd62aea972d351f1c51f6","tid":1279263,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:37:11.000Z","msg":"作為後生既，好簡單咁講幾句比各位前輩聽：<br />\n<br />\n1. 今日既年青一代係你教出黎既，就算唔係你教出黎，都係係你地打拼出黎既土壤入面成長。<br />\n當年若果唔係你地令到香港經濟起飛，今時今日既後生仔點樣騰出手腳爭取民主自由？你地既貢獻，不亞於今日我地既付出。<br />\n<br />\n2. 請千祈唔好自責點解當年幫唔到我地向英國佬爭取，你地冇欠左我地。每一個世代都有自己既目標，當年一代係為兩餐晏仔，今日一代就係為左生而為人既尊嚴、自由。<br />\n<br />\n3. 請唔好覺得你地乜都幫唔到後生仔。論體力、論自己既經濟重擔同家室，傻既都知唔夠後生仔黎。其實得閒黎同我地傾下計講下粗口，認識下傾下計，講下當年點溝女，又知下乜野叫「假膠」、「直必腸」、「燒山好野」，share下我地既長輩圖係Facebook, Whatsapp，已經比左我地莫大既支持。同埋你會發覺後生一代同平時差好遠，上到網係好多野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 如果係為左一個共同目標，唔需要分乜野輩份年齡。不論長幼老少，大家都係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次見到咁多位上黎玩，我自己就真係好驚訝又開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望你地係連登玩得開心，實現番林鄭既競選口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794507388cae55da364a900f243c27d3af21bdc5","tid":1279263,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:37:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd8ac4964c4d48d2f7f26a6302f951c580c6101a","tid":1279263,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:38:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25c1e5e11a04df59416d1d3956fa78143776a522","tid":1279263,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:39:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9db242528d4c3563c947d6db83a10c55d2c3ee70","tid":1279263,"uid":99018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:44:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b735164be66c4d6b1f859a03395598ead495a72c","tid":1279263,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:10:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5b53537bb80d4d71c9e714f2906c884a43584fd","tid":1279263,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:41:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5e6cfb5e2cd5893cac656f9b12529003f7a6ea8","tid":1279263,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:21:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"546977462caad35729e61f2579f66b43c90b58cc","tid":1279263,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:23:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b394d7e9a2b0d9e0d61655a34bad7e7659b6f5f","tid":1279263,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:54:19.000Z","msg":"推"}]}